in, S., Rothrock, D., Steele, M., Assimilating satellite concentration data into an Arctic sea ice mass balance model (1996) J. Geophys. Res, 101 G (9), pp. 20849-20868. , 1979-1985; Thorndike, A.S., Colony, R., (1980) Arctic Ocean Bugy Program, , Seattle, WA. University of Washington. Polar Science Center. (Data Report); Wismann, V., A G-band wind scatterometer model derived from the data obtained during the ERS 1 calibration/validation campaign (1992) Proceedings of the First ERS-I Symposium Space at the Service of Our Environment, 1, pp. 55-59. , In Kaldeich B., ed. 4-5 November, Cannes, France Paris, European Space Agency. (ESA Special Publ. SP-359.)","Weaver, R.L.S.; Cooperative Inst. Res. Envi. Sci., University of Colorado, Department of Geosciences, Boulder CO 80309, United States",,,,,,,,02603055,,,,"English","Ann. Glaciol.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-0034512265
